Class PantryModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301.recipebot.model.PantryModel

  • public class PantryModel
extends java.lang.Object
    This class communicates with the DatabaseHelper asynchronousy to post updates to it's receivers UI -> Model -> Database.
